These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-1::.
City: san-francisco, berlin
There are 2 different favourite colors: apricot, ebony
1. the person who likes apricot is on the far left##1
2. the person who likes ebony is not the person traveling to berlin##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | berlin   | san-francisco  |
| Sport   | apricot | ebony |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-2::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: metal, indie
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: satire, family
1. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
2. the person watching satire movies is not the fan indie##6

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1   |     2      |
| Food   | metal | indie      |
| Pet    | satire  | family |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-3::.
2 different pets are kept: cat, fish
There are 2 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, lemonade
1. the owner of the fish is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
2. the person drinking soy-milk is not the owner of the cat##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |
| Food    | fish  | cat    |
| Sport   | soy-milk | lemonade |

